reviewText: Supposed to come with a slip-cover (to enhance the relatibility of it), an excellent cut of a 'very' good film with a full menu. Content is vivid, historical, very entertaining and great for engaging your mind in a standard sci-fi manner. Military in Stargate media is cliche' mid-70's and a form of entertainment in its own right...
Excellent movie with added scenes.  Extra features were great!
